name: CVE-2020-14723
description: Vulnerability in the Oracle Help Technologies product of Oracle Fusion Middleware (component: Web UIX). Supported versions that are affected are 11.1.1.9.0 and 12.2.1.3.0. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle Help Technologies. Successful att CVE project by @Sn0wAlice
